(27, '[TEST] Lielborne Manor', 'test-lielborne-manor', '<p>Welcome to <strong>Lielborne Manor</strong>! Our family, with the first meeting with this place, developed its special chemistry of feelings. Both with the crooked balcony and green-painted stairs of the Lielborne manor\'s house, its still overgrown but unusually beautiful park, the swift Borne river, the collapsed bridges, the drained mill pond and the majestic Daugava, full of sedges. We also observe this in our relatives and friends, so we hope that it will happen to you too, and you will become our frequent guest!</p>', NULL, 242, 10, 'Latvian - Belarus Border (Silene - Urbany), Saliena, Augšdaugava 5469, Latvia', NULL, NULL, 8, 1, '245,243,244,', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2000000.00, '12:00AM', '12:00AM', NULL, NULL, 'publish', 9, 9, NULL, '2023-09-14 00:33:23', '2023-09-14 00:41:49', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, 2, NULL, NULL),
