(82, 22, 'page', 1, 'Terms and conditions for Virtuard LTD', 'Virtuard is a platform based on advertisements and virtual tours that can be attached to your advertisement for anyone and any type who wants to use this service. \r\nBefore proceeding, however, it is better to say a few words to explain what the Virtual Tour is.\r\n \r\nThe virtual tour is an interactive experience that allows you to virtually explore an environment or location without having to be physically present on site. It can be used in many situations, for example:\r\n\r\nTourism: Virtual tours can be used to promote tourist destinations, allowing visitors to virtually explore places such as hotels, museums, parks and tourist attractions.\r\nReal Estate: Virtual tours can help sell or rent real estate by giving potential buyers or tenants the chance to preview the inside of the house or apartment.\r\nEducation: Virtual tours can be used to provide students with an interactive view of places such as museums, natural parks and archaeological sites.\r\nCommercial: Companies can use virtual tours to showcase their offices, shops or factories to potential customers or business partners.\r\nEngineering and architecture: Engineering and architecture firms can create 360 ​​renderings for the design, giving the client an innovative way to visit the work before it is built \r\n\r\nIn general, virtual tours are used to offer an engaging and immersive experience to users, who can virtually explore an environment in a realistic and interactive way.\r\nVirtuard allows you to build them independently simply by following the specific tutorial but let\'s see the advantages in detail.', 227, '{\"facebook\":{\"title\":null,\"desc\":null,\"image\":null},\"twitter\":{\"title\":null,\"desc\":null,\"image\":null}}', 11, 11, NULL, NULL, '2023-10-10 19:37:48', '2023-10-10 19:44:48'),
